{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, each player puts the top card of their deck into their shields face down. Then choose one of your opponent's shields and put it on the bottom of its owner's deck.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ At the end of each of your turns, you may look at the top 3 cards of your deck. If you do, put one of them into your hand and the rest into your graveyard.
■ At the end of each of your turns, if there are 8 or more creatures that have different costs in your graveyard, you may put all of them into the battle zone.

